22:31.451 --> 22:33.184
Welcome to my parish.

22:33.186 --> 22:35.252
I am Father Elias.

22:36.189 --> 22:39.290
May I show you around, hm?

22:41.561 --> 22:43.661
Come with me, please.

22:48.568 --> 22:53.604
(birds chirping)
(dog barking)

23:02.181 --> 23:05.015
Your feet, are you sure you
don't want the sandals, hm?

23:05.985 --> 23:06.884
No?

23:14.627 --> 23:17.428
(doors creaking)

23:21.634 --> 23:24.769
(footsteps thudding)

23:31.778 --> 23:34.845
(people chattering)

23:37.683 --> 23:40.451
So, you take charity

23:40.453 --> 23:42.520
without offering
anything in return, hm?

23:43.723 --> 23:45.156
