23:45.158 --> 23:47.625
this church can't
afford to spare.

23:47.627 --> 23:50.261
An honest man would want
to return the favor, huh?

23:51.631 --> 23:56.500
I need this place swept,
you do it and we're even.

23:59.105 --> 23:59.937
Hm?

24:00.840 --> 24:02.673
It's not complicated.

24:04.877 --> 24:08.112
You know it is said,
I am a benevolent man.

24:09.148 --> 24:11.782
But I am also a
practical one, my son.

24:12.952 --> 24:15.619
(gentle music)

24:17.423 --> 24:20.224
(birds chirping)

24:28.801 --> 24:31.602
(broom swishing)

24:39.712 --> 24:42.780
(footsteps tapping)

24:48.221 --> 24:50.087
I'm not the kind to take charity

24:50.089 --> 24:52.857
from a stranger without
giving an offer.

24:54.160 --> 24:57.995
You swept and I want to offer
you something in return.

25:00.500 --> 25:01.398
