something to receive.

26:15.274 --> 26:16.740
- Yes, that's a great idea.

26:16.742 --> 26:18.509
I'll make my stew.

26:18.511 --> 26:20.711
- Esther, perfecto.

26:20.713 --> 26:22.813
(speaking in foreign language)

26:22.815 --> 26:24.949
- I will do that, Father.

26:27.353 --> 26:29.019
